{"id": "19062", "post": "<div class=\"post-19062 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers category-tutorials tag-centos-7 tag-mysql tag-ngnix tag-php tag-vps-confgiuration\" id=\"post-19062\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lemp-stack-installation-on-centos-7/\" rel=\"bookmark\">LEMP Stack installation on Centos 7</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/centos-7/\" rel=\"tag\">CentOS 7</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/mysql/\" rel=\"tag\">mysql</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ngnix/\" rel=\"tag\">NGNIX</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/php/\" rel=\"tag\">PHP</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/vps-confgiuration/\" rel=\"tag\">vps confgiuration</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> April 29, 2019 @ 4:33 pm, by Frank Williams</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><h2><strong>What is a LEMP STACK?</strong></h2><p>Linux an open source operating, is most popular OS among web hosting providers. For successfully hosting a website on a Linux server we need four important software components i.e an operating system, a web server, a database server and a platform to run our website codes to display web pages. These four components support each other and makes up a <strong>LEMP STACK</strong>.</p><p>LEMP Stack is the most widely used web server configuration for developing and hosting websites and web applications.</p><p>The 4 common components that makes up a STACK are:</p><ol><li><strong>Linux</strong>: Operating system</li><li><strong>Nginx </strong>(pronounced as \u201cengine X\u201d): Web server</li><li><strong>MariaDB</strong>: Database server</li><li><strong>PHP</strong>: Scripting language to run codes/scripts to display web pages.</li></ol><p><strong>So, what is the use of this information?</strong></p><p>Well, if you are going to host a website you will be needing a SERVER and a server without LEMP Stack installed is not going to server the purpose.</p><p>In this article I will be demonstrating how to prepare your Linux Server for successfully hosting a website.</p><p><span id=\"more-19062\"></span></p><h2><strong>Prerequisites</strong></h2><p>Before you begin with the installation of LEMP stack following things are required:</p><ol><li>VPS or Dedicated server with Centos 7 installed.</li><li>Root login details or a user login with sudo privileges.</li></ol><p><strong><em>Let\u2019s begin with the Installation!</em></strong></p><h2><strong><u>NGINX</u></strong></h2><p>Follow the steps given below for installing NGINX on Centos 7</p><ol><li>Update your server just to make sure all the packages are up-to date</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>yum update -y</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1-300x76.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19064 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1-300x76.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"430\" height=\"109\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1-300x76.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1.png 729w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1-300x76.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1.png 729w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></pre><ol start=\"2\"><li>Using any text editior create a file \u201cnginx.repo\u2019 at location \u201c/etc/yum.repos.d/\u201d</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>vi /etc/yum.repos.d/nginx.repo</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2-300x39.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19065 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2-300x39.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"438\" height=\"57\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2-300x39.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2.png 761w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2-300x39.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2.png 761w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></pre><p>And add the following content in the file:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>[nginx]\n\nname=nginx repo\n\nbaseurl=http://nginx.org/packages/mainline/centos/7/$basearch/\n\ngpgcheck=0\n\nenabled=1</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3-300x75.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19066 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3-300x75.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"112\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3-300x75.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3.png 750w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3-300x75.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/3.png 750w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><ol start=\"3\"><li>Update your server again and install NGINX</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>yum update\n\nyum install nginx</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4-300x66.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19067 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4-300x66.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"432\" height=\"95\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4-300x66.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4.png 736w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4-300x66.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/4.png 736w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MzciIGhlaWdodD0iMTM0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDM3IDEzNCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19068\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/5-300x92.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"134\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/5-300x92.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/5-768x235.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/5-1024x314.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/5.png 1352w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\"></p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MzkiIGhlaWdodD0iMTk5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDM5IDE5OSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19069\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6-300x136.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"439\" height=\"199\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6-300x136.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6-768x347.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6.png 871w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\"></p><ol start=\"4\"><li>Start NGINX and enable it on server reboot.</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl start nginx\n\nsystemctl enable nginx</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MzMiIGhlaWdodD0iMTMiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA0MzMgMTMiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19070\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/7-300x9.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"13\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/7-300x9.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/7.png 725w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 433px) 100vw, 433px\"></p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MzciIGhlaWdodD0iNTEiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA0MzcgNTEiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19071\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/8-300x35.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"51\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/8-300x35.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/8-768x88.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/8.png 773w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\"></p><ol start=\"5\"><li>Check the Status of NGINX</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl status nginx</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0NDgiIGhlaWdodD0iMTM2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDQ4IDEzNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19072\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/9-300x91.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"136\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/9-300x91.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/9-768x233.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/9.png 776w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\"></pre><p>NGINX is now successfully installed!</p><p>You can now verify whether NGINX is working fine or not by directly accessing your server\u2019s IP on the browser as shown below:</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>http://server_domain_name_or_IP/</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0NDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTA3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDQwIDEwNyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19073\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/10-300x73.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"107\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/10-300x73.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/10-768x187.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/10-1024x249.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/10.png.webp 1124w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\"></pre><p>You will see the default NGINX webpage as shown in the image below:</p><p>NOTE: If the default NGINX page is not loading in the browser then you need to allow port 80 in the server\u2019s default FIREWALL.</p><p>Run the following commands to allow port 80 in FIREWALL:</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>firewall-cmd \u2013permanent \u2013add-port=80/tcp\n\nfirewall-cmd \u2013reload</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0OTMiIGhlaWdodD0iOTciIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA0OTMgOTciPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19074\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/11-300x59.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"493\" height=\"97\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/11-300x59.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/11.png 737w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\"></p><h2><strong><u>MariaDB</u></strong></h2><p>It is the database server used for creating and managing databases used by your websites and web applications.</p><ol><li>Install Mariadb and MySQL/MariaDB-PHP support</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>yum install mariadb-server php-mysql -y</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NTIiIGhlaWdodD0iOTIiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NTIgOTIiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19075\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/12-300x50.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"92\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/12-300x50.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/12.png 735w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\"></pre><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NTYiIGhlaWdodD0iODkiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NTYgODkiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19076\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/13-300x48.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"556\" height=\"89\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/13-300x48.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/13-768x123.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/13-1024x164.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/13.png 1343w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\"></p><ol start=\"2\"><li>Start MariaDB and enable it on server reboot.</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl start mariadb\n\nsystemctl enable mariadb</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MzMiIGhlaWdodD0iODciIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1MzMgODciPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19077\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/14-300x49.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"533\" height=\"87\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/14-300x49.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/14.png 756w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\"></p><ol start=\"3\"><li>Secure your MariaDB server.</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>mysql_secure_installation</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre></pre><p>It will ask for the root password, just press \u201c<strong>enter</strong>\u201d as there is no password initially.</p><p>After this prompt will ask to set a new password. Press <strong>Y</strong> and set the new password.</p><p>Answer <strong>Y</strong> at the following prompts:</p><ul><li>Remove anonymous users?</li><li>Disallow root login remotely?</li><li>Remove test database and access to it?</li><li>Reload privilege tables now?</li></ul><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MTQiIGhlaWdodD0iNDgwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTE0IDQ4MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19078\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/15-300x280.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"514\" height=\"480\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/15-300x280.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/15.png 749w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 514px) 100vw, 514px\"></p><ol start=\"4\"><li>MariaDB is now secured and you can access SQL shell using the following command:</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>mysql -u root -p</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre>When prompted, enter the MariaDB password you have set in step 3.</pre><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MjUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTI2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTI1IDEyNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19079\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/16-300x72.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"126\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/16-300x72.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/16.png 750w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\"></p><h2><strong><u>PHP</u></strong></h2><ol><li>Install PHP and PHP-FPM (FastCGI Processing Manager)</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>yum install php php-fpm -y</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NDEiIGhlaWdodD0iODMiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NDEgODMiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19080\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/17-300x46.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"83\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/17-300x46.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/17.png 737w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 541px) 100vw, 541px\"></pre><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NDQiIGhlaWdodD0iNDkiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NDQgNDkiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19081\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/18-300x27.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"49\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/18-300x27.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/18-768x69.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/18-1024x92.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/18.png 1316w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 544px) 100vw, 544px\"></p><ol start=\"2\"><li>Start and enable PHP-FMP on reboot</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl start php-fpm\n\nsystemctl enable php-fpm\n\nsystemctl status php-fpm</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><h2><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NTciIGhlaWdodD0iMTY3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTU3IDE2NyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19082\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/19-300x90.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"167\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/19-300x90.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/19-768x229.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/19.png 877w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 557px) 100vw, 557px\"></h2><h2><strong><u>Secure the PHP setup</u></strong></h2><ol><li>Using any text editor open the file \u201c/etc/php.ini\u201d (main php configuration file</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>vi /etc/php.ini</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NTUiIGhlaWdodD0iNzQiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NTUgNzQiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19083\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20-300x40.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"555\" height=\"74\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20-300x40.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20.png 733w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 555px) 100vw, 555px\"></pre><ol start=\"2\"><li>Search for the parameter \u201ccgi.fix_pathinfo=1\u201d.</li></ol><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NDQiIGhlaWdodD0iMTE2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTQ0IDExNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19085\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22-300x64.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"116\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22-300x64.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22.png 588w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 544px) 100vw, 544px\"></p><p>Uncomment it by removing the semicolon and replace it with \u201c<strong>cgi.fix_pathinfo=0</strong>\u201d.</p><p>The final result should like as shown in the screenshot below:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NDQiIGhlaWdodD0iMTE2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTQ0IDExNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19085\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22-300x64.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"116\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22-300x64.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/22.png 588w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 544px) 100vw, 544px\"></p><ol start=\"3\"><li>Save and close the file.</li></ol><p>We did this because \u201ccgi.fix_pathinfo=1\u201d is an insecure setting as it tells PHP to try to execute the closest file it can find if the actual PHP file does not match exactly. By setting \u201c<strong>cgi.fix_pathinfo=0</strong>\u201d we are actually mitigating the possibility of the execution of an arbitrary php code if the requested .php file is not present in the server.</p><ol start=\"4\"><li>By default, PHP runs under Apache user i.e. \u201cnobody\u201d. Since you have installed NGINX as the web server you need to change the User and Group to match with the NGINX\u2019s User and Group.</li></ol><p>NGINX uses \u201cnginx\u201d as the User and Group.</p><p>So, open the file \u201c/etc/php-fpm.d/<u><a href=\"http://www.conf\">www.conf</a></u>\u201d using any text editor.</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>vi /etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iMTA3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTY0IDEwNyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19086\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/23-300x57.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"107\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/23-300x57.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/23.png 748w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\"></pre><p><strong>And replace user = apache and group = apache TO user = nginx and group = nginx</strong> as shown in the screenshots below:</p><p>Before the making changes.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NzAiIGhlaWdodD0iOTUiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NzAgOTUiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19087\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/24-300x50.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"570\" height=\"95\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/24-300x50.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/24.png 612w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"></p><p>After making the changes.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NzEiIGhlaWdodD0iMTIwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTcxIDEyMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19088\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/25-300x63.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"571\" height=\"120\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/25-300x63.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/25.png 514w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\"></p><ol start=\"5\"><li>Save and close the file.</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"6\"><li>Restart PHP-FPM</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl restart php-fpm</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><strong><u>Configure NGINX to Process PHP Pages</u></strong></pre><ol><li>Disable the default NGINX configuration file.</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>mv /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf.back</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1ODkiIGhlaWdodD0iMTA2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTg5IDEwNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19089\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/26-300x54.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"589\" height=\"106\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/26-300x54.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/26-768x137.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/26.png 785w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 589px) 100vw, 589px\"></pre><ol start=\"2\"><li>Create a new configuration file at location \u201c/etc/nginx/conf.d/\u201d. Here i am creating a file with the name \u201cnewnginx.conf\u201d</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>vi /etc/nginx/conf.d/newnginx.conf</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1ODkiIGhlaWdodD0iMTA0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTg5IDEwNCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19090\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/27-300x53.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"589\" height=\"104\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/27-300x53.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/27.png 737w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 589px) 100vw, 589px\"></pre><p>And paste the following content in the newly created nginx configuration file and save it:</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>server {\n\nlisten&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 80 default_server;\n\nlisten&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [::]:80 default_server;\n\nserver_name&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>&nbsp;your_domain_or_IP</em></strong>;\n\nroot&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; /var/www/html;\n\nindex&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; index.html;\n\n\n\n\nlocation / {\n\ntry_files $uri $uri/ =404;\n\n}\n\n\n\n\nlocation ~* \\.php$ {\n\nfastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\n\ninclude&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fastcgi_params;\n\nfastcgi_param&nbsp;&nbsp; SCRIPT_FILENAME&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\n\nfastcgi_param&nbsp;&nbsp; SCRIPT_NAME&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $fastcgi_script_name;\n\n}\n\n}</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>NOTE</strong>: <strong><em>replace \u201cyour_domain_or_IP\u201d with your actual domain name or server\u2019s IP address.</em></strong></p><ol start=\"3\"><li>Restart NGINX</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>systemctl restart nginx</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><strong><u>Testing PHP Processing In Your Server</u></strong></pre><ol><li>In order to test whether PHP is configured and working fine or not we will test it by creating a php script. For this create a file using any text editor with the name \u201cinfo.php\u201d at location \u201c/var/www/html\u201d</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>vi /var/www/html/info.php</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NjAiIGhlaWdodD0iOTkiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA1NjAgOTkiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19091\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/28-300x53.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"99\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/28-300x53.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/28.png 737w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\"></pre><p>And paste the following code in \u201cinfo.php\u201d file and save it:</p><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>&lt;?php\n\nphpinfo();\n\n?&gt;</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><p>So, the file will look as shown in the screenshot attached below:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NjMiIGhlaWdodD0iMTIyIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTYzIDEyMiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19092\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/29-300x65.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"122\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/29-300x65.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/29.png 736w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\"></p><ol start=\"2\"><li>You can now verify whether PHP is working fine or not by directly accessing your server\u2019s IP on the browser as shown below:</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>http://server_domain_name_or_IP/info.php</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre>You will the see the page as shown in the screenshot below:</pre><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1NjkiIGhlaWdodD0iMTg2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTY5IDE4NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19093\" data-src=\"http://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/30-300x98.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"569\" height=\"186\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/30-300x98.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/30-768x252.png.webp 768w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/30-1024x336.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/30.png.webp 1158w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 569px) 100vw, 569px\"></p><p>This page basically gives you information about your server from the perspective of PHP.</p><ol start=\"3\"><li>Remove the info.php file once you have confirmed that PHP is working fine.</li></ol><table width=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"602\"><pre>rm /var/www/html/info.php</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><pre></pre><p><strong><em>Congratulations! LEMP stack is now successfully installed.</em></strong></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flemp-stack-installation-on-centos-7%2F&amp;t=LEMP%20Stack%20installation%20on%20Centos%207\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=LEMP%20Stack%20installation%20on%20Centos%207&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flemp-stack-installation-on-centos-7%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flemp-stack-installation-on-centos-7%2F&amp;title=LEMP%20Stack%20installation%20on%20Centos%207&amp;mini=true\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-linkedin dpsp-no-label dpsp-last\" title=\"Share on LinkedIn\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span 